{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154690/extras/steam-content-header-Bitmates.gif?t=1737476674\" /><br><strong>Embark on Your Epic Adventure in the World of Bitmates!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into <strong>Bitmates</strong>, a vibrant MMORPG where every choice you make shapes your destiny. Explore a vast fantasy world teeming with life, uncover its secrets, and craft your legend in a player-driven economy. Whether you're mastering life skills, taking down legendary bosses, or socializing with friends, Bitmates is the adventure you've been waiting for.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154690/extras/steam-feature-bitmates-04_Explore__gather2.gif?t=1737476674\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Explore a Vast, Beautiful World</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From lush forests to arid deserts, explore a rich world with many environments, each crafted with love and detail. Discover hidden treasures, tackle unique challenges, and immerse yourself in the pixel-perfect art of this expansive world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154690/extras/steam-feature-bitmates-04_Master_Variety.gif?t=1737476674\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Master Every Skill</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bitmates offers many skills for you to perfect. From fishing in serene lakes to forging powerful gear, every action contributes to your character's progression. With independent skill systems and endless synergies, your mastery defines your journey.   </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154690/extras/steam-feature-bitmate_Express_yourself.gif?t=1737476674\" /><strong>Create Your Unique Identity</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Express yourself with a vast collection of cosmetics. Stand out in the crowd with rare outfits and accessories, earned through gameplay or traded in the player-driven economy. Whether you\u2019re a heroic warrior or a mystical alchemist, your style is your own.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154690/extras/steam-feature-bitmate_Epic_boss_battles.gif?t=1737476674\" /><strong>Face Epic Boss Battles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Test your mettle against colossal foes in thrilling, strategic combat. Whether solo or with allies, these encounters offer rare rewards and the chance to prove your skill. Are you ready to take on the challenge?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154690/extras/steam-feature-bitmate_Daily_missions_with_colourful_NPCs.gif?t=1737476674\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Engage with a World Full of Stories</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into a rich history with unique NPCs and quests. Help villagers, uncover ancient mysteries, and make decisions that shape the world around you. Every region tells its own story\u2014what role will you play?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154690/extras/steam-feature-bitmates_make_friends.gif?t=1737476674\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Forge Lifelong Friendships</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bitmates thrives on community. Join friends for group activities, celebrate achievements, or simply relax in the serene towns. With vibrant social hubs, there\u2019s always someone to share your adventure.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_it